---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="Mission and methodology for JobScope.">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <p><strong>About JobScope</strong></p>
    <h1>Practical career clarity for students and switchers.</h1>
    <p>
      JobScope collects structured, experience-based job stories to help people make better
      education and career decisions.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="stack">
    <article class="panel">
      <h2>Mission</h2>
      <p>
        Show what jobs actually look like in daily practice, including tradeoffs, workflows, and
        realistic advice.
      </p>
    </article>
    <article class="panel">
      <h2>How content is collected</h2>
      <p>
        Contributors complete a structured form. Required fields ensure each story includes
        actionable detail rather than vague opinions.
      </p>
    </article>
    <article class="panel">
      <h2>Trust model</h2>
      <p>
        All submissions are reviewed manually before publishing. Contributor identity can be public
        or anonymous, clearly labeled on each profile.
      </p>
    </article>
  </section>
</Layout>
